text: Raúl Alberto Romero (born March 11, 1935) is a retired Argentine wrestler. He competed at the 1964 Summer Olympics both in freestyle and Greco-Roman wrestling, but lost all his matches. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Olympic wrestlers of Argentina Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Argentine male sport wrestlers Category:1935 births
